The paper is about an API for building distributed machine learning algorithms, which suggests that it could fit into several sub-categories. "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) is the most likely category, as the paper is primarily focused on developing machine learning algorithms. "cs.DC" (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and "cs.DS" (Data Structures and Algorithms) are also likely categories, as the paper discusses the challenges of building distributed algorithms and the need for data-centric computing. "cs.Distributed" (Distributed Computing) is another possible category, as the paper is specifically about building distributed machine learning algorithms. Finally, "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category, as the paper is about developing algorithms for machine learning, which is a subfield of AI.
